AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000419> "2009/10/19 Alan Ruttenberg. Named 'junk' relation useful in restrictions, but not a real instance relationship"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000419> "quality is specified as"@en)

# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000293> (has specified input)

