# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000538> (bulk)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000538> "bulk"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000538> "The bulk is a fiat object part that describes the volume or mass of material considered as a whole, often in contrast to surface or interface phenomena."@en)
