# Class: <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000124> (symmetry equivalency assertion)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000124> "DO NOT INITIALIZE THIS CLASS OR ANY OF THIS SUBCLASSES
The symmetry equivalency assertion class is meant to enable assertions of  crystollograhpic equivalence between single crystallographic direction /plane and family of directions/planes if the equivalence applies for the given crystal symmetry. This class is part of the \"inference engine\""@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000124> "symmetry equivalency assertion"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(owl:deprecated <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000124> "true"^^xsd:boolean)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000124> "Symmetry equivalency assertion is an information content entity which is used to infer crystallographic equivalence between single crystallographic direction /plane and family of directions/planes if the equivalence applies for the given crystal symmetry."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000124> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000030>)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000124> ObjectUnionOf(ObjectIntersectionOf(ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002351> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000020>) ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000152> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000021>) ObjectAllValuesFrom(<https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000152> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000021>)) ObjectIntersectionOf(ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002351> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000022>) ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000152> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000023>) ObjectAllValuesFrom(<https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000152> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000023>))))
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000124> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000158> <https://w3id.org/pmd/cryo/CRYO_0000028>))

