AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020117> "A state where the bonds between entities transmit shear forces."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0000060> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020117> "true"^^xsd:boolean)

# Individual: <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020118> (aggregate state liquid)

